data.title: Bebra
data.words: Chieftain - the leader of the Cossacks. Minotaur - Cretan monster with the body of a man and the head of a bull, who lived in a Labyrinth and was killed by Theseus. Scimitar - bladed stabbing and slashing edged weapon with a long single-edged blade having a double bend; something between a saber and a cleaver.
